text: My Name is Kerry Durkin I look after
sales recruitment mainly into Europe but

South Africa as well the most exciting
part about working here at AWS is

get on really well with everybody
everyone is there to help you out if
you're stuck on something you're not
quite sure what to do my team helps me
grow just by being there for me when I
have to put my hand up especially as
we're still working virtually most of
the time everyone's super responsive
someone will say put five minutes in my
diary and I'll go through it with you
when I Was preparing for the interview
everyone was like oh the leadership
principles you've really got to prepare
for the leadership principles we live by
them and I was like oh okay great and
then when I started working here I did
realize that actually everybody does
live and Breathe by our leadership
principles it's not just a this is our

and I love that I love that about
working here at AWS
